At the moment the log in screen can't be customised. However as an Administrator I would like to modify it, e.g.:
- add a link to my email so that my users know to contact me to have an account set up;
- add my company logo and adjust the colours.

{panel}
17/Dec/2014: This is now available on all Atlassian Cloud sites.

Follow the instructions in [Setting up Google Apps for your site|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/Cloud/Setting+up+Google+Apps+for+your+site] to get started.
{panel}

Need to update Google Apps integration as existing API is being deprecated.

{panel:title=Atlassian Cloud SAML single sign-on}
SAML single sign-on is available as part of Identity Manager. [More information about Identity Manager|https://www.atlassian.com/enterprise/cloud/identity-manager].
 
[Read up on how to configure SAML single sign-on for our Cloud products|https://confluence.atlassian.com/x/bJlCMw].
 
Thanks for all of your feedback and discussion on this ticket. We'll continue to monitor and respond to it, as well as take on board your requests for future enhancements.
 
We receive a lot of requests for new features and improvements, so if you'd like to better understand how we make roadmap decisions, please read: [https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DEV/Implementation+of+New+Features+Policy]{panel}
